featured_reviews.review_id:
Har masjid ka aik apna hi ambience hota hai aur masjid wo jagah hai jaha sukoon milta hai maine is masjid me boht saari acchi cheeze dekhi maine aaj dehradoon me is masjid me namaze zohar ke dauran kuch boht acchi baate paayi jinhe mai points me ralh raha hu:
1.majid ki building boht khubsurat aur mashallah boht badi thi
2.masjid me 2 baitul khala aur lamba wazu khana hai
3.kuch bacche safo ki safai karte hue mile
4.saaf safai ka boht accha khyaal rakha gya tha
5.aur sabse acchi chiz mujhe waha ki ghadi lagi jisme boht saari details thi jaise namaz ki kaza ka waqt azaan ke waqt tareek wagairah

Over all mujhe boht accha laga is masjid me namaz padhkar bas mujhe aik chiz aur chahunga ki waha par ho wo hai wazu ka pani saaf karne ke liye aik tauliya.

Shukriya

Jama Masjid Doon is believed to have been constructed by Aurangzeb. The Masjid is said to have been build as a makeshift place of worship for the artisans sent by the Mughal king to build the Guru Ram Rai Durbar.

It is good for God Lovers Experience Seeker
